{"tid":2114613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試與試戴","createTime":"2020-07-19T03:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T03:41:08.000Z","uid":63901,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de94905ae2dcc477bdeb49ba3bb85068296ce28f","tid":2114613,"uid":63901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:37:28.000Z","msg":"依家市面大部分口罩都標籤 防粉塵 防花粉 防飛沫等 有賴口罩中層嘅聚丙烯熔噴不織布 抵擋病毒飛沫傳播<br />\n<br />\n今日剪咗一d測試 撕開睇下有冇絲 同埋做吸唔吸到紙碎的靜電測試 全部會測試3次<br />\n<br />\n另外 亦因為屋企人對口罩質料比較敏感 特別天氣熱嘅時候 所以都會選擇一d唔會有毛毛的口罩 下面果d口罩全部都自己試戴過四粒鍾 希望幫到大家㨂口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下測試六款口罩<br />\n<br />\nP=Pass, F=Fail, N/A=Not applicable<br />\n1.黐到碎紙3秒 唔會跌落嚟<br />\n2.可以戴4小時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1t4ekT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1t4ekT.jpg&h=82188d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.同舟口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8p7b8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8p7b8f.jpg&h=c2dbf60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDd0w8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDd0w8M.jpg&h=8e5eee07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試：P<br />\n試戴測試：P<br />\nRemark：戴嘅時候感覺冇氣 唔透氣<br />\n<br />\n2.Face Armor<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zwtF4o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zwtF4o.jpg&h=719abc5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n9jKYQ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn9jKYQ7.jpg&h=0a3831a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試：P<br />\n試戴測試：F<br />\nRemark：只戴兩小時 鼻樑位鬆 下巴鬆 空氣隨便入<br />\n<br />\n3.DGC<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxFm05u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxFm05u.jpg&h=5b742b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXRtF5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXRtF5x.jpg&h=62db24be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試：P<br />\n試戴測試：F<br />\nRemark：只戴5分鐘 鼻好痕癢 耳繩非常緊 要拉鬆<br />\n<br />\n4.Yohm<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyB9qx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyB9qx4.jpg&h=0ed36645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4koDiS7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4koDiS7.jpg&h=db8c8bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試：P<br />\n試戴測試：P<br />\nRemark：戴全日<br />\n<br />\n5.Bethreis<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gk2LyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gk2LyT.jpg&h=d1a55cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1qm5JkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1qm5JkB.jpg&h=d7d37323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試：P<br />\n試戴測試：F<br />\nRemark：只戴10分鐘 好痕好痕<br />\n<br />\n6.香港特別行政區同心抗疫口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f95qJmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff95qJmy.jpg&h=85c02086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1Ku91C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1Ku91C.jpg&h=0c2d0ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聚丙烯熔噴不織布測試：P<br />\n試戴測試：P<br />\nRemark：戴6小時 一家10隻<br />\n<br />\n總結：家母一日三四粒鍾係室外工作 特別天氣嚴熱嘅時候 口罩出毛 掃到鼻孔 導致不斷流鼻水 <br />\n由3月疫情至今 己經買咗十幾盒 由一百二十蚊到二百幾都有 有d仲一買買兩盒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果見到人真係覺得口罩痕 借一隻你覺得好嘅比佢試戴下吖 一定幫到佢好多<br />\n<br />\n希望大家買到合適嘅口罩 特別依家每日多60幾單 唔好因為痕癢 有時要除口罩落黎捽鼻 戴下唔戴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3a1aa8976405f9d919a7db4b69f742ce0d577c","tid":2114613,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"幾時試埋大陸口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}